high_descs: Turn to the left and find the small table.
Pick up the pencil from the small table, on the left side.
Carry the pencil and turn to the left, then left again. Face the coffee table on the left side.
Place the pencil on the coffee table, in between the two boxes of tissues.
Turn to the left and then right to find the table on the left. Face the table in the corner.
Pick up the pencil from the right side.
Carry the pencil and turn to the left, then left again and face the coffee table on the left.
Place the pencil on the coffee table, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room.
Pick up the pencil on the table.
Turn right and take two steps, then turn left and take three steps, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Place the pencil on the coffee table.
Turn left and take two steps, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the white pencil on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and take two steps, then turn left to face the table.
Put the white pencil on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the pencils to the table.

high_descs: turn left and walk to the small brown table at the end of the room
pick the pencil up off of the desk
turn around and walk over to the right side of the coffee table in front of the couch
place the pencil down on top of the coffee table
turn left and walk over to the table in the corner of the room up ahead
pick up the pencil off of the table there
turn left and walk back over to the right side of the coffee table
place the pencil down on the table next to the other pencil
anns.task_desc: place two pencil's down on the coffee table
